  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice. Factual stub. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">A native visual SVG editor (Tauri + Vue) — draw rectangles, circles, and paths on a canvas and edit each element's geometry through a properties inspector. Part of the <a href=\"/tag/vulpes-nvim\" class=\"internal-link text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\">Vulpes Nvim</a> toolset.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The element inspector — live geometry editing for each SVG primitive\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/vulpesvg/code.png\" alt=\"The element inspector — live geometry editing for each SVG primitive\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/vulpesvg/code.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/vulpesvg/code.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/vulpesvg/code.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/vulpesvg/code.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The element inspector — live geometry editing for each SVG primitive\" width=\"1400\" height=\"900\" style=\"--splay-rot:-1.38deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1400×900\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The element inspector — live geometry editing for each SVG primitive</figcaption>\n</figure>",
